description:
**Biological Science Certification Required**

 **EFFECTIVE:** 2024-2025 School Year

 **QUALIFICATIONS:**

* Valid New Jersey Instructional Certificate (CE, CEAS, Provisional, or Standard) with Biological Science Endorsement (2210);
* Demonstrated knowledge of NJ Student Learning Standards in subject specialty and effective teaching methods;
* Knowledge of Next Generation Science Standards;
* Ability to conduct/facilitate inquiry-based laboratory investigations;
* Ability to maintain a positive learning environment;
* Strong interpersonal and communication skills;
* Required criminal history background check and proof of U.S. citizenship or legal resident alien status.

 **REPORTS TO:** Principal

 **SALARY:** As per salary guide

 **TERMS OF EMPLOYMENT****:** 10-month position

